trans-unit.source: Represents the AppSequence header defined in the April 2005 version of the WS-Discovery Protocol.
trans-unit.target: 表示在 Ws-discovery 协议 2005 年 4 月版本中定义的 AppSequence 标头。

trans-unit.source: This class allows a receiver of discovery messages to process those messages in order even though they were received out of order.
trans-unit.target: 此类允许发现消息处理这些消息按顺序，即使它们已在按顺序接收的接收器。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.VersionApril2005.DiscoveryMessageSequenceApril2005"></xref> class from the specified <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.VersionApril2005.DiscoveryMessageSequenceApril2005"></xref>从指定的类<xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence"></xref>实例。

trans-unit.source: Gets the schema for the AppSequence header for the April 2005 version of the WS-Discovery protocol.
trans-unit.target: 获取 Ws-discovery 协议 2005 年 4 月版本的 AppSequence 标头的架构。

trans-unit.source: The schema for the AppSequence header.
Gets the schema for the AppSequence header for the April 2005 version of the WS-Discovery protocol and adds it to the specified schema set if the schema set does not already contain the schema.
trans-unit.target: 获取 Ws-discovery 协议 2005 年 4 月版本的 AppSequence 标头的架构并将其添加到指定的架构集中如果架构集中尚未包含架构。

trans-unit.source: The XML qualified name of the schema.
trans-unit.target: 架构的 XML 限定的名称。

trans-unit.source: Reads a discovery message sequence from XML.
trans-unit.target: 从 XML 中读取发现消息序列。

trans-unit.source: The XML reader to read from.
trans-unit.target: 要从其中进行读取的 XML 读取器。
